  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage the Cinema Schedule!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know your audience well and showcase hit movies at the right times! Plan the showtimes carefully to fill your halls and increase customer satisfaction. It's up to you to choose which movies to release each week; set your strategy wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maintain Order!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There may be those who want to disrupt the peace in the cinema hall! Detect and intervene with smokers and those secretly recording films. Be quick, or other customers may leave due to dissatisfaction. Keep order by slapping and ensure all customers are happy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Popcorn & Drink Service</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No cinema experience is complete without warm popcorn and cold drinks! Increase customer satisfaction by offering the tastiest snacks. Remember, every service takes you a step ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Team, Achieve Success!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Managing the cinema empire alone can be tough. Hire and grow your team to enhance customer satisfaction. The right employees will elevate your service quality to the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage the Cinema Schedule!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to know your audience well and showcase hit movies at the right times! Plan the showtimes carefully to fill your halls and increase customer satisfaction. It's up to you to choose which movies to release each week; set your strategy wisely!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f6d29ea070b88c4a0cf51cef41dfffc3.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Maintain Order!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There may be those who want to disrupt the peace in the cinema hall! Detect and intervene with smokers and those secretly recording films. Be quick, or other customers may leave due to dissatisfaction. Keep order by slapping and ensure all customers are happy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/f58dae0ad4c17786f0ee1564d34a3bd4.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Popcorn & Drink Service</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No cinema experience is complete without warm popcorn and cold drinks! Increase customer satisfaction by offering the tastiest snacks. Remember, every service takes you a step ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/66b5c6a44e94d1aae04119cda43ed648.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Team, Achieve Success!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Managing the cinema empire alone can be tough. Hire and grow your team to enhance customer satisfaction. The right employees will elevate your service quality to the top!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.poster.avif?t=1771968123\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.webm?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098070/extras/c0acbb1833cbb3a1ccd7960de8d7d1dd.mp4?t=1771968123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
